<section id="tutorials" class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 text-base font-medium text-indigo-600 bg-indigo-50 rounded-full mb-4">
        专业教程
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">从入门到精通的智能体教程</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600">
        无论您是初学者还是专业开发者，这里都有适合您的智能体应用与创建教程。
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <!-- Application Tutorials -->
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-100">
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 mb-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-indigo-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
            <i data-lucide="book-open" class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-600"></i>
