            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <span class="text-3xl font-light text-indigo-600">02</span>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-medium mb-1">知识库搭建与优化</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2">深入了解如何为智能体构建高质量的知识库，提升回答准确性。</p>
              <a href="#" class="text-xs text-indigo-600 hover:underline">立即学习 →</a>
